95
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:15,294
What...

96
00:08:15,294 --> 00:08:16,863
..happened to me yesterday?

97
00:08:16,863 --> 00:08:17,763
Well, yesterday..

98
00:08:17,763 --> 00:08:20,766
