And, why do I have to?

110
00:08:59,739 --> 00:09:01,307
There's gotta be something

111
00:09:01,307 --> 00:09:03,009
Why do you always keep messing with him?

112
00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:07,847
Okay!

113
00:09:09,181 --> 00:09:11,150
In that case, if you won't tell,

114
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,019
I'm going to post on social media

115
00:09:13,019 --> 00:09:15,721
..that the chef here serves their customers poorly
- Wait a minute

116
00:09:15,721 --> 00:09:18,724
Everyone has to know that this place doesn't....
- Wait, please, wait..

117
00:09:19,659 --> 00:09:22,662
Chef Mochi can only remember a day at a time and...

118
