125
00:09:58,297 --> 00:10:00,866
..neither can he remember his past

126
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:05,137
Today's events can only be remembered today

127
00:10:14,447 --> 00:10:17,450
Having memories for only a day?

128
00:10:17,450 --> 00:10:19,452
Is that possible?

129
00:10:21,253 --> 00:10:22,521
Kim!

130
00:10:22,521 --> 00:10:24,190
What are you doing?

131
00:10:29,295 --> 00:10:30,830
Do you think

132
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:32,665
there can be a person that

133
00:10:32,665 --> 00:10:34,734
can only have memories for a day,

134
00:10:34,734 --> 00:10:38,371
and forget everything when they wake up the next day?

135
00:10:40,339 --> 00:10:42,408
If you wanna know, it's not that hard

136
00:10:47,013 --> 00:10:50,883
Does a person who loses both short term and long term memory,

137
00:10:50,883 --> 00:10:55,187
but only has memories of deach present day exist?

138
00:10:57,490 --> 00:11:01,193
It is a very rare condition, but there are real reports, with two main categories

139
00:11:01,193 --> 00:11:02,895
1. Trauma to the nervous system

140
00:11:02,895 --> 00:11:05,898
which occur after brain surgery when the brain lacks oxygen

141
00:11:05,898 --> 00:11:08,067
or when there is damge to the hippocampus

142
00:11:08,067 --> 00:11:10,503
With examples such an English musician,

143
00:11:10,503 --> 00:11:13,606
who can't tell the day or month, but remembers his wife

144
00:11:13,606 --> 00:11:15,207
2. Psychological Trauma

145
00:11:15,207 --> 00:11:17,209
which occurs for immense emotional distress

146
00:11:17,209 --> 00:11:19,345
such as being triggered emotionally

147
00:11:19,345 --> 00:11:21,180
Some cases forget their whole identity

148
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,215
or important situations in life

149
00:11:23,215 --> 00:11:25,985
There have been cases where subjects can only recall new experiences for a short period

150
00:11:25,985 --> 00:11:28,487
and forget. Like a complete reset

151
00:11:30,022 --> 00:11:31,824
Chef Mochi..

152
00:11:31,824 --> 00:11:34,093
..has a problem with his brain

153
00:11:34,093 --> 00:11:35,861
He can't remember his past,

154
00:11:35,861 --> 00:11:39,565
Today's events can only be remembered today

155
00:11:40,633 --> 00:11:42,368
But..

156
00:11:42,368 --> 00:11:44,003
