but just then I saw them call your name

280
00:23:40,482 --> 00:23:42,451
But...

281
00:23:42,451 --> 00:23:44,253
..have we ever met each other?

282
00:23:44,253 --> 00:23:46,321
Why...

283
00:23:46,321 --> 00:23:49,324
..do I draw your portrait

284
00:23:49,324 --> 00:23:50,826
You...

285
00:23:50,826 --> 00:23:52,227
..drew my portrait?

286
00:23:56,398 --> 00:23:59,401
He just brings people to cook

287
00:23:59,401 --> 00:24:01,603
You don't know him or anything

288
00:24:21,189 --> 00:24:25,060
Wishing you a safe journey today. Hope everything goes smoothly

289
00:24:25,060 --> 00:24:27,696
See you again

290
00:24:27,696 --> 00:24:34,102
Next time, if you come again, I’ll take you to cook Thai food

291
00:24:35,537 --> 00:24:39,875
I love Thai food

292
00:24:39,875 --> 00:24:41,543
Thai Sour Curry

293
00:24:41,543 --> 00:24:43,011
Kang Som

294
00:24:43,045 --> 00:24:44,513
Delicious

295
00:24:44,513 --> 00:24:46,481
Yeah, yeah you’re Thai now

296
00:24:46,481 --> 00:24:47,716
Bye

297
00:24:47,816 --> 00:24:49,051
Have a nice day

298
00:24:49,518 --> 00:24:51,820
- Thank you so much, bro. I'll get your commission later
- Sure!

299
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,789
Bring her again!

300
00:24:58,093 --> 00:25:00,128
Kim's pretty good, Dad

301
00:25:00,128 --> 00:25:02,064
Don't let him overstep his postion

302
00:25:02,064 --> 00:25:04,333
Next time, why don't you just let him do it?

303
00:25:13,375 --> 00:25:14,643
Sang!

304
00:25:14,643 --> 00:25:17,279
I've sent off the client now,

305
00:25:17,279 --> 00:25:20,215
if you need anything next time, let me know

306
00:25:20,215 --> 00:25:21,883
Then next time don't get involved

307
00:25:21,883 --> 00:25:23,719
I can do my own job!

308
00:25:27,723 --> 00:25:30,726
Just stay put till the year is done and just leave

309
00:25:30,726 --> 00:25:32,494
What a sleaze

310
00:25:36,565 --> 00:25:39,568
We could've said things nicely, Sang

311
00:25:39,568 --> 00:25:42,571
I'm here to help, for goodness sake

312
00:26:14,136 --> 00:26:17,439
Oh? Why are you here so fast?

313
00:26:18,373 --> 00:26:20,108
Didn't you say you had a shift today?

314
00:26:20,609 --> 00:26:22,377
You told me to hurry up!

315
00:26:22,377 --> 00:26:25,013
I thought you were stressed about something

316
00:26:25,981 --> 00:26:27,616
At first, I was stressed

317
00:26:27,616 --> 00:26:30,619
But after seeing your face, it's all gone

318
00:26:35,157 --> 00:26:37,492
Don't tell me you brought a surgical knife out?

319
00:26:38,226 --> 00:26:40,429
Is this the time to be teasing?

320
00:26:40,429 --> 00:26:42,531
So what's your problem?

321
00:26:45,067 --> 00:26:46,868
Well, since we're here..

322
00:26:53,141 --> 00:26:54,543
You read my mind

323
00:26:54,543 --> 00:26:56,178
- Alright, let's go
- Alright

324
00:27:01,817 --> 00:27:02,884
Doctor...

325
00:27:04,619 --> 00:27:07,522
These days, Tao Sor seems to remember things a lot more

326
00:27:07,522 --> 00:27:10,959
You're afraid Tao Sor's gonna remember the things you don't want him to, right?

327
00:27:15,864 --> 00:27:19,935
Tao Sor remembering isn;t an easy thing, you know?

328
00:27:19,935 --> 00:27:23,705
He has to be exposed to the same situation for a good length of time

329
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:28,944
Or maybe, something could've triggered his brain

330
00:27:30,779 --> 00:27:33,048
So what could've triggered him?

331
00:27:33,048 --> 00:27:35,851
Um, electric currents,

332
00:27:35,851 --> 00:27:38,019
..intense physical trauma,

333
00:27:41,923 --> 00:27:44,459
What about a person?

334
00:27:44,459 --> 00:27:46,428
A person?

335
00:27:48,330 --> 00:27:51,333
This, I'm not sure

336
00:27:53,068 --> 00:27:56,037
Either way, can you come see Tao Sor often for the time being?

337
00:27:56,037 --> 00:28:00,408
In case something happens, and you could quickly tell me

338
00:28:00,408 --> 00:28:02,177
Can do

339
00:28:03,411 --> 00:28:05,080
But you gotta treat me to dinner tonight

340
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:07,482
I'll get a you huge order of lobster

341
00:28:07,482 --> 00:28:09,050
One this big

342
00:28:10,385 --> 00:28:12,888
- Okay, cheers!
- Cheers!

343
00:28:36,378 --> 00:28:40,816
Tao Sor, my name's Dr. Kleun, your on hand doctor

344
00:28:40,816 --> 00:28:43,819
I probably don't have to introduce myself, do I?

345
00:28:45,654 --> 00:28:48,657
Everyone remembers me...

346
00:28:48,657 --> 00:28:51,660
...but I can't remember anyone

347
00:28:51,660 --> 00:28:54,129
Are you a real doctor? I don't even know

348
00:29:04,239 --> 00:29:06,341
This picture...

349
00:29:06,341 --> 00:29:08,043
is the first drawing you did

350
00:29:24,259 --> 00:29:26,528
And this one,

351
00:29:26,528 --> 00:29:29,531
is of the place you like to go exercise at

352
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:35,203
Even if you tell me, I still wouldn't remember

353
00:29:37,706 --> 00:29:39,574
Even if you can't remember things,

354
00:29:39,574 --> 00:29:43,645
it doesn't mean that you can't live life

355
00:29:43,645 --> 00:29:45,380
Doctor?

356
00:29:46,548 --> 00:29:49,117
Do I have a chance to remember everyone?

357
00:29:49,117 --> 00:29:52,053
I still wake up and recall

358
00:29:52,053 --> 00:29:54,456
how much my parents love me

359
00:29:55,490 --> 00:29:57,559
what I did at the beach,

360
00:30:01,663 --> 00:30:04,366
I want to have memories like everyone else

361
00:30:10,438 --> 00:30:13,441
Whether or not you remember anything,

362
00:30:13,441 --> 00:30:16,444
I want to let you know,

363
00:30:16,444 --> 00:30:20,148
that everyone in your family loves and cares for you very much

364
00:30:20,148 --> 00:30:24,586
and they'll take care of you, no matter what happens

365
00:30:50,845 --> 00:30:53,848
Hello, Siw?

366
00:30:53,848 --> 00:30:56,851
What's up?

367
00:31:01,423 --> 00:31:04,426
Okay, I'll be there

368
00:31:22,143 --> 00:31:25,947
Next time, if you need me to pick you up, you can just tell me

369
00:31:27,148 --> 00:31:29,217
Could I?

370
00:31:29,217 --> 00:31:32,687
Of course! I'm your cousin, after all!

371
00:31:32,687 --> 00:31:34,122
Yeah?

372
00:31:34,122 --> 00:31:37,459
I've never felt that way

373
00:31:37,459 --> 00:31:39,694
You sure are blunt

374
00:31:39,694 --> 00:31:43,765
It's true! When you were here, I was still really young

375
00:31:43,765 --> 00:31:45,500
How could I remember anything

376
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:48,737
And you never came back to visit again

377
00:31:48,737 --> 00:31:51,039
How could I feel that way?

378
00:31:51,039 --> 00:31:53,742
My mom, she...

379
00:31:53,742 --> 00:31:55,744
has some bad history with this place

380
00:31:56,578 --> 00:31:59,047
So my family never came back

381
00:32:00,582 --> 00:32:02,250
Then, no problem

382
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:05,253
We can just get close now, don't you think?

383
00:32:12,727 --> 00:32:14,629
You serving me curry too?

384
00:32:14,629 --> 00:32:16,865
Just the broth is enough!

385
00:32:16,865 --> 00:32:20,468
Let's see, if you want the fish so much

386
00:32:20,468 --> 00:32:22,270
then go ahead!

387
00:32:22,270 --> 00:32:23,972
So you could be smart like everyone else

388
00:32:23,972 --> 00:32:27,108
What? I'm already smart!

389
00:32:27,108 --> 00:32:29,644
There! Eat some vegetables too!

390
00:32:31,980 --> 00:32:33,448
I guess so...

391
00:32:38,486 --> 00:32:39,287
Siw!

392
00:32:41,289 --> 00:32:44,292
About Sang...

393
00:32:45,427 --> 00:32:49,931
...when did she become so cold hearted?

394
00:32:51,499 --> 00:32:56,237
That case? She's actually very sensitive, you know?

395
00:32:56,237 --> 00:33:02,677
But when she's in front of Dad, she has put on a strong act

396
00:33:09,317 --> 00:33:12,620
In that case, you can take care of the bill

397
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:15,623
Wait, wait, wait. Did you get me out here to treat you dinner?

398
00:33:24,899 --> 00:33:27,902
You still enjoy Orange Curry, don't you?

399
00:33:29,704 --> 00:33:31,239
I don't like it

400
00:33:31,239 --> 00:33:36,144
Sang makes us have Orange Curry for breakfast, lunch and dinner

401
00:33:39,013 --> 00:33:43,251
What else would you have me eat? All I have everyday is Orange Curry

402
00:33:43,251 --> 00:33:46,254
Well, aside from Sang, you also have me

403
00:33:46,888 --> 00:33:48,756
I raised you off of Orange Curry

404
00:33:48,756 --> 00:33:52,227
Wait for it, a whole year full of Orange Curry for sure

405
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:02,003
Kim, we gotta go. Get the bill!

406
00:34:02,003 --> 00:34:03,805
What's going on, I haven't eaten yet!

407
00:34:03,805 --> 00:34:05,106
Hurry up and eat!

408
00:34:05,106 --> 00:34:07,509
Waiter? Get us the bill!

409
00:34:15,617 --> 00:34:18,620
Hello, Ms. Suli, thank you for the stars

410
00:34:18,620 --> 00:34:22,023
you sent a whole star shower, that's so nice! Thank you!

411
00:34:24,492 --> 00:34:28,696
Okay everyone, we're now gonna go into the horoscopes for Leos

412
00:34:28,696 --> 00:34:32,400
This week, fortune for love will be strong!

413
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:34,569
You might just meet the one

414
00:34:43,044 --> 00:34:44,245
But...

415
00:34:44,779 --> 00:34:49,317
You have to put in a little effort, you can't just sit around being pretty

416
00:34:49,317 --> 00:34:51,853
You might meet someone who hurts you

417
00:34:56,624 --> 00:35:00,962
What can I do to see the person I like? We're in different places

418
00:35:00,962 --> 00:35:04,499
They're an influencer that does fortune telling,

419
00:35:04,499 --> 00:35:07,936
and I'm an influencer doing lifestyle content in Phuket

420
00:35:10,305 --> 00:35:13,341
If you want to see her, you have to go to her

421
00:35:13,341 --> 00:35:17,545
you’ll have to find a way to make her come to you

422
00:35:17,545 --> 00:35:19,981
And since she’s an influencer

423
00:35:19,981 --> 00:35:24,919
using work as a reason would probably be the most effective

424
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:28,423
Do you want me to help think of a solution?

425
00:35:29,224 --> 00:35:32,227
No need, I think I figured it out

426
00:35:37,465 --> 00:35:40,268
As for Virgos,

427
00:35:40,268 --> 00:35:44,572
your luck in romance might not be so good

428
00:36:14,102 --> 00:36:15,303
Yes, Mom?

429
00:36:15,303 --> 00:36:19,374
Kim! Why don't ever call me? Are you okay?

430
00:36:20,008 --> 00:36:23,011
I'm just pretty busy, Mom

431
00:36:24,612 --> 00:36:27,615
And how are you doing?

432
00:36:30,318 --> 00:36:33,321
If you want to know, why don't you come see for yourself?

433
00:36:33,321 --> 00:36:37,292
Meaning, I'll take you here for a vacation

434
00:36:37,292 --> 00:36:43,197
Umm, and have you visited the deity I told you to?

435
00:36:43,197 --> 00:36:52,707
Oh Mom, if the master's advice really worked, I probably wouldn't have to be dealing with all this here

436
00:36:52,707 --> 00:36:55,710
Can I just come home?

437
00:36:55,710 --> 00:36:56,878
Is something going on?

438
00:36:56,878 --> 00:37:00,615
You can tell me, I'll take of it

439
00:37:02,050 --> 00:37:05,820
Well...there's nothing going on, Mom

440
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:11,159
I'm going to bed now. Good night

441
00:38:17,725 --> 00:38:20,728
Gradually start breathing to the rhythm of my voice

442
00:38:20,728 --> 00:38:24,699
Let your heart be free

443
00:38:50,709 --> 00:38:53,712
Kim! Where you going so early?

444
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:59,718
I thinking of getting something to eat

445
00:39:08,727 --> 00:39:13,232
Oh, Sang. We're about to enter low season

446
00:39:13,232 --> 00:39:17,569
I was thinking if getting some influencers to promote our boat would be good?

447
00:39:17,569 --> 00:39:19,738
I think it's a waste

448
00:39:19,738 --> 00:39:23,709
Another thing, if we're entering the monsoon season, there still wouldn't be any clients

449
00:39:24,276 --> 00:39:25,677
Siw!

450
00:39:25,677 --> 00:39:27,212
I like your idea

451
00:39:27,212 --> 00:39:28,447
- Really?
- Yeah!

452
00:39:28,447 --> 00:39:30,616
Are you going to use it to promote your own business?

453
00:39:33,619 --> 00:39:35,754
And why do we have to promote others?

454
00:39:38,791 --> 00:39:41,527
Just promote the family's boat

455
00:39:41,527 --> 00:39:43,796
So that means you're in?

456
00:39:45,297 --> 00:39:47,132
Come up with a plan of action then

457
00:39:47,132 --> 00:39:49,434
so I can present it to Dad

458
00:39:49,434 --> 00:39:50,669
Will do!

459
00:39:54,206 --> 00:39:56,708
And don't accepting any work elsewhere

460
00:41:23,729 --> 00:41:25,831
Are you drawing me right now?

461
00:41:34,439 --> 00:41:37,442
If it's not okay with you, I can get rid of it

462
00:41:39,244 --> 00:41:41,546
Just wait a minute

463
00:41:41,546 --> 00:41:43,015
It looks good

464
00:41:43,015 --> 00:41:44,483
Let me take it

465
00:41:44,483 --> 00:41:46,652
I'll buy it off you

466
00:41:46,652 --> 00:41:47,753
I won't sell

467
00:41:47,753 --> 00:41:49,054
What are you, an indie artist?

468
00:41:49,888 --> 00:41:53,191
But if you want it, I could give it to you

469
00:41:54,793 --> 00:41:56,995
Sure. Then...

470
00:41:56,995 --> 00:41:58,730
..sign it for me too,

471
00:41:58,730 --> 00:42:01,400
in case you get famous one day and I could sell it

472
00:42:02,801 --> 00:42:04,770
Alright..

473
00:42:05,737 --> 00:42:07,372
Wanna go surfing?

474
00:42:09,641 --> 00:42:12,644
Nah, I don't know how

475
00:42:13,412 --> 00:42:15,280
If you can't, then you should try learning!

476
00:42:16,081 --> 00:42:19,084
Come on, I'll show you how it's done

477
00:42:26,725 --> 00:42:29,728
I've never been in the ocean

478
00:42:33,999 --> 00:42:37,002
Are you afraid of the ocean?

479
00:42:43,575 --> 00:42:50,615
Try it out, I'll bring you out there. Trust me

480
00:43:08,433 --> 00:43:11,136
Is that really a good idea?

481
00:43:11,136 --> 00:43:12,404
Why?

482
00:43:14,006 --> 00:43:16,375
I've never been in the ocean before

483
00:43:18,844 --> 00:43:22,514
In that case, there might be another way

484
00:43:22,514 --> 00:43:24,950
What way?

485
00:43:24,950 --> 00:43:26,852
I'll show you

486
00:43:40,732 --> 00:43:45,771
I don't know if you've been here or not, but I think

487
00:43:45,771 --> 00:43:50,042
this place will make you feel like the ocean isn't a scary place

488
00:43:51,443 --> 00:43:53,478
Ready?

489
00:43:57,482 --> 00:43:59,217
Scared?

490
00:44:07,292 --> 00:44:10,295
Gradually start breathing to the rhythm of my voice

491
00:44:10,295 --> 00:44:14,232
Let your heart be free

492
00:44:14,232 --> 00:44:17,169
Breath in,

493
00:44:17,169 --> 00:44:20,172
breathe out

494
00:44:20,172 --> 00:44:23,075
Breath in,

495
00:44:23,075 --> 00:44:25,043
breathe out

496
00:44:25,043 --> 00:44:27,412
Breath in,

497
00:44:27,412 --> 00:44:30,415
breathe out

498
00:44:48,867 --> 00:44:51,870
Now let's go inside

499
00:44:51,870 --> 00:44:54,873
If it's too much, close your eyes

500
00:45:03,815 --> 00:45:06,818
Follow me, okay?

501
00:45:12,357 --> 00:45:16,728
Another step, go foward a little

502
00:45:20,098 --> 00:45:23,068
And now, open your eyes

503
00:46:11,850 --> 00:46:15,587
You see? Inside, it's breathtaking

504
00:47:54,486 --> 00:47:59,791
the bottom is kinda pretty, don't you think?

505
00:48:22,478 --> 00:48:27,716
In Bangkok, I barely had any time to go anywhere

506
00:48:27,716 --> 00:48:30,719
So I came to the aquarium in secret alot

507
00:48:37,593 --> 00:48:42,064
I don't know if I've been here before either

508
00:48:43,465 --> 00:48:47,035
I might have, but..

509
00:48:47,035 --> 00:48:50,038
I probably don't remember

510
00:48:56,512 --> 00:48:59,515
Aren't you curious why?

511
00:49:03,051 --> 00:49:05,854
Let me tell you a secret

512
00:49:05,854 --> 00:49:10,292
Actually, you and I have met before

513
00:49:16,265 --> 00:49:19,968
Alright, I've told you my secret

514
00:49:19,968 --> 00:49:23,505
Now, it's your turn

515
00:49:32,080 --> 00:49:35,083
My secret is...

516
00:49:37,352 --> 00:49:39,988
I can't remember yesterday's events

517
00:49:39,988 --> 00:49:43,725
But I can remember some pieces

518
00:49:44,593 --> 00:49:48,063
Like cooking,

519
00:49:48,063 --> 00:49:51,033
drawing, but...

520
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:55,170
You saying that we know each other,

521
00:49:55,170 --> 00:49:58,507
I don't know if it's true

522
00:50:00,609 --> 00:50:03,946
Then...

523
00:50:03,946 --> 00:50:06,281
what else do you remember?

524
00:50:06,281 --> 00:50:09,284
Tell me about it

525
00:50:16,191 --> 00:50:18,527
Oh!

526
00:50:18,527 --> 00:50:21,530
I really like Tao Sor snacks

527
00:50:21,530 --> 00:50:24,867
and I also like drawing

528
00:50:25,901 --> 00:50:27,870
I think I'm afraid of the ocean

529
00:50:27,870 --> 00:50:31,607
But...

530
00:50:31,607 --> 00:50:33,642
Now I'm not afraid anymore

531
00:50:33,642 --> 00:50:36,912
Because...

532
00:50:36,912 --> 00:50:42,184
the bottom is kinda pretty, don't you think?

533
00:52:01,029 --> 00:52:01,697
Nown!

534
00:52:11,707 --> 00:52:12,374
I'm here.

535
00:52:22,050 --> 00:52:24,319
The cards really that bad?

536
00:52:26,254 --> 00:52:29,024
To be honest, yes.

537
00:52:29,024 --> 00:52:30,359
Both in your job and in your love life.

538
00:52:30,359 --> 00:52:32,794
Whatever you hope for, you won't receive.

539
00:52:32,794 --> 00:52:35,197
Whatever you hope against, you won't receive.

540
00:52:36,331 --> 00:52:41,136
So why did you have me promote your family's business?
